{
  "texts": [
    "Jinfa Huang is a Ph.D. student in the Department of Computer Science, University of Rochester (UR), advised by Prof. Jiebo Luo.",
    "He aims at building multimodal interactive AI systems that can not only ground and reason over the external world signals.",
    "As steps towards this goal, His research interests include but are not limited to multimodal understanding and multimodal generation.",
    "Prior to that, he got his master's degree from Peking University (PKU) in 2023, advised Prof. Jie Chen.",
    "Yunjun Shi is currently a PhD student in the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, National University of Singapore, advised by Prof. Vincent Y. F. Tan."
  ]
}